2015年7月，吉尔访问了[[韩国|韩国]]、{{tsl|en|越南||越南}}、[[老挝|老挝]]和[[日本|日本]]四国，宣传女性教育和军人家庭权益。访日期间，她还参加了“支持军队”行动的活动，以支持军人、老兵及其家属的权益。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.stripes.com/news/pacific/jill-biden-to-promote-education-military-families-in-asia-1.357152|title=Jill Biden to promote education, military families in Asia|publisher=Stars & Stripes|date=2015-07-09|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2020-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605041408/https://www.stripes.com/news/pacific/jill-biden-to-promote-education-military-families-in-asia-1.357152|dead-url=no}}</ref>在任第二夫人的同时，吉尔仍在北弗吉尼亚社区学院任教。2015年秋季学期时，她全心投入教育事业，共教授五门课程。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2015-08-21/jill-biden-is-planning-a-full-teaching-load-for-the-fall|title=Jill Biden Is Planning a Full Teaching Load for the Fall|publisher=Bloomberg|date=2015-08-21|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2017-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216055027/https://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2015-08-21/jill-biden-is-planning-a-full-teaching-load-for-the-fall|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年2月，吉尔和丈夫拜登一起参加了“癌症登月计划”（{{lang|en|Cancer Moonshot 2020}}）的全国巡回活动。这一计划由拜登领导，此前他们的长子博·拜登和其他几位家人就因癌症逝世，吉尔称其对此有“个人情感”。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sfgate.com/bayarea/article/Biden-visits-UCSF-to-talk-with-cancer-survivors-6858318.php|title=Joe Biden, wife hold cancer roundtable at UCSF|publisher=San Francisco Chronicle|date=2016-02-29|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2016-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320102710/http://www.sfgate.com/bayarea/article/Biden-visits-UCSF-to-talk-with-cancer-survivors-6858318.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年3月，吉尔还主持了欢迎仪式，迎接美国宇航员{{le|斯科特·凯利 (宇航员)|Scott Kelly (astronaut)|斯科特·凯利}}在太空环游一年后返回地球。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.upi.com/Top_News/US/2016/03/03/Jill-Biden-gifts-Scott-Kelly-with-beer-apple-pie-on-return-to-US/8731457006269/|title=Jill Biden gifts Scott Kelly with beer, apple pie on return to U.S.|publisher=UPI|date=2016-03-03|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2016-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160321220930/http://www.upi.com/Top_News/US/2016/03/03/Jill-Biden-gifts-Scott-Kelly-with-beer-apple-pie-on-return-to-US/8731457006269/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年1月20日，[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]接任第45任美国总统，其副手[[迈克·彭斯|迈克·彭斯]]出任第48任副总统。拜登夫妇出席了[[2017年美國總統就職典禮|就职典礼]]，正式卸任。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/2017/live-updates/politics/live-coverage-of-trumps-inauguration/michelle-obama-jill-biden-introduced/|title=Trump inauguration live coverage|publisher=Washington Post|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024093253/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/2017/live-updates/politics/live-coverage-of-trumps-inauguration/michelle-obama-jill-biden-introduced/|dead-url=no}}</ref>两人在典礼结束后乘[[美铁|火车]]离开华盛顿回到特拉华州的家乡。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2017/01/20/politics/biden-train-ride-trnd/index.html|title=After 8,200 round-trip train rides, Joe Biden heads home|publisher=CNN|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123022807/https://edition.cnn.com/2017/01/20/politics/biden-train-ride-trnd/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2017/01/20/biden-returns-delaware-amtrak-inauguration/96840088/|title=Joe Biden leaves D.C. on -- what else? -- Amtrak|publisher=USA Today|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204185915/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2017/01/20/biden-returns-delaware-amtrak-inauguration/96840088/|dead-url=no}}</ref>吉尔在之前接受采访时曾表示自己期待在卸任后“能再次享受一点独立空间”，尤其终于可以自己开车、独自跑步。<ref name="today"/>

