hive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929013457/https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/joe-jill-biden-reported-earning-15-million-income/story?id=64225419 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，而这一段时间夫妇俩也积极向慈善组织捐款<ref name="abc-income" />。

