月，为{{tsl|en|Newport News Apprentice School|纽波特新闻学徒学校}}毕业班学生演讲<ref>{{cite news | url=https://pilotonline.com/news/local/article_3746bfe6-37b9-11e9-b5b9-1f7a2cb6efcd.html | title=Jill Biden tells Apprentice School graduates, 'You are a master of a craft, a shipbuilder and a leader.' | first=Peter | last=Dujardin | date=2019-02-23 | newspaper=The Virginian-Pilot | access-date=2019-03-09 | archive-date=2019-04-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401143050/https://pilotonline.com/news/local/article_3746bfe6-37b9-11e9-b5b9-1f7a2cb6efcd.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

