2019年，拜登继续在北弗吉尼亚社区学院教书，她曾告诉记者，自己在采访的空当忙着给论文打分<ref name="dt-talks-book" />。在{{tsl|en|2020 Iowa Democratic caucuses|2020年艾奥瓦州民主党党团会议|艾奥瓦州}}等选情激烈的州份，她独自出席竞选活动，有时会带孙女上台<ref>{{cite news | url=https://whotv.com/2019/06/28/jill-biden-visits-iowa-supporters-react-to-joe-bidens-debate-performance/ | title=Jill Biden Visits Iowa; Supporters React to Joe Biden's Debate Performance | date=2019-06-28 | first=Monica | last=Madden | publisher=WHO-TV | access-date=2019-06-30 | archive-date=2019-06-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630113045/https://whotv.com/2019/06/28/jill-biden-visits-iowa-supporters-react-to-joe-bidens-debate-performance/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。她在新罕布什尔州竞选活动中曾这样劝说大家让拜登胜出：“你们要知道，你们的候选人在医保方面可能做得比乔好，但是你们要看看谁会赢得这场选举，到那时你们或许会咽点口水，想着‘好吧，我个人觉得谁谁谁更好’，但底线必须是我们要打败特朗普<ref>{{cite news | url=https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/458027-jill-biden-tells-voters-to-pick-husband-your-candidate-may-be-better-on | title=Jill Biden tells voters to pick husband: 'Your candidate may be better' on some policies, but 'we have to beat Trump' | first=Justin | last=Wise | newspaper=The Hill | date=2019-08-19 | access-date=2019-09-28 | archive-date=2019-09-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190928170533/https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/458027-jill-biden-tells-voters-to-pick-husband-your-candidate-may-be-better-on | dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

儿子[[亨特·拜登|亨特·拜登]]因[[特朗普-乌克兰丑闻|特朗普-乌克兰丑闻]]成为共和党政客的关注焦点后，吉尔出面发声：“亨特没做错事情，这是底线”<ref name="nyt-why" />。后来在{{tsl|en|Impeachment trial of Donald Trump|唐纳德·特朗普弹劾案审判}}中，南卡罗来纳州参议员[[林賽·格雷厄姆|林賽·格雷厄姆]]反复要求让亨特·拜登作目击者证词，让他和吉尔的友谊正式破裂<ref>{{cite news | url=https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/jill-biden-longer-considers-gop-sen-lindsey-graham/story?id=68726067 | title=Jill Biden says she no longer considers GOP Sen. Lindsey Graham a friend | author-first=Shoshana | author-last=Dubnow | publisher=ABC News | date=2020-02-03 | access-date=2020-02-16 | archive-date=2020-02-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215234715/https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/jill-biden-longer-considers-gop-sen-lindsey-graham/story?id=68726067 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

此次竞选活动，吉尔显得要比乔前两次竞选活动要活跃<ref name="wapo-finally">{{cite news | url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/jill-biden-is-finally-ready-to-be-first-lady-can-she-help-her-husband-beat-trump/2020/08/17/acacc936-e007-11ea-8181-606e603bb1c4_story.html | title=Jill Biden is finally ready to be first lady. Can she help her husband beat Trump? | author-first=Jada | author-last=Yuan | author2-first=Annie | author2-last=Linskey | newspaper=The Washington Post | date=2020-08-17 | access-date=2020-08-19 | archive-date=2020-08-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819145936/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/jill-biden-is-finally-ready-to-be-first-lady-can-she-help-her-husband-beat-trump/2020/08/17/acacc936-e007-11ea-8181-606e603bb1c4_story.html | deadurl=no }}</ref>。在不情愿之下，吉尔于2020年春季学期从北弗吉尼亚社区学院休假，全职投入竞选活动<ref name="nyt-why">{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/01/us/politics/joe-jill-biden-2020.html | title=In Iowa, a Former Second Lady Campaigns to Be the First | author-first=Katie | author-last=Glueck | author2-first=Steve | author2-last=Eder | newspaper=The New York Times | date=2020-02-02 | page=A16 | access-date=2020-02-12 | archive-date=2020-07-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719231401/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/01/us/politics/joe-jill-biden-2020.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2019冠狀病毒病美國疫情|2019冠狀病毒病美國疫情]]期间，她学习[[教育技术学|网络授课]]<ref name="wapo-finally" />，还表示即便丈夫当选，她也会继续在社区学院教书<ref name="wapo-finally" />。

距艾奥瓦州党团会议还有几个星期，吉尔在该州出席造势活动的次数，有时比乔还要多<ref name="nyt-why" />。她向选民公开自己专用于竞选活动的电子邮箱，让选民给她提问题<ref name="wapo-closer" />。在两人共同出席的场合，吉尔会给拜登接话，显示出“更亲民”的形象<ref name="wapo-closer">{{cite news | url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2020/01/16/jill-biden-tries-close-deal-her-husband-one-tiny-iowa-town-time/ | title=Jill Biden tries to close the deal for her husband, one tiny Iowa town at a time | author-first=Holly | author-last=Bailey | newspaper=The Washington Post | date=2020-01-16 | access-date=2020-02-13 | archive-date=2020-05-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200523173836/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2020/01/16/jill-biden-tries-close-deal-her-husband-one-tiny-iowa-town-time/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月3日{{tsl|en|Results of the 2020 Democratic Party presidential primaries#Super Tuesday|2020年美国总统选举民主党初选|超级星期二}}初选中，吉尔在乔讲话的时候，突然站起身，伸直手推开向他抗议的人士<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.tampabay.com/news/nation-world/2020/03/04/were-jill-biden-and-symone-sanders-the-real-winners-of-super-tuesday-twitter-thinks-so/?utm_expid=.rZxRlJI0T86fmAabR1Jv8w.0&utm_referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bing.com%2F | title=Were Jill Biden and Symone Sanders the real winners of Super Tuesday? Twitter thinks so | author-first=Daniel | author-last=Figueroa IV | newspaper=Tampa Bay Times | date=2020-03-04 | access-date=2020-03-14 | archive-date=2020-10-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008170021/https://www.tampabay.com/news/nation-world/2020/03/04/were-jill-biden-and-symone-sanders-the-real-winners-of-super-tuesday-twitter-thinks-so/?utm_expid=.rZxRlJI0T86fmAabR1Jv8w.0&utm_referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bing.com%2F | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年6月，乔·拜登预计成为民主党总统候选人，吉尔出版童书《乔·拜登的故事》（''Joey: The Story of Joe Biden''）。该书将乔描绘成“勇敢、有冒险精神”的孩子，尽管因为口吃经常被同伴欺负<ref>{{cite magazine | url=https://people.com/politics/dr-jill-biden-talks-her-new-campaign-trail-project-and-what-she-learned-about-her-husband/ | title=Dr. Jill Biden on Her Campaign Trail Project & What She Wants People to Know About Her Husband | author-first=Sam | author-last=Gillette | author2-first=Ally | author2-last=Mauch | date=2020-06-30 | magazine=People | access-date=2020-07-05 | archive-date=2020-07-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705195034/https://people.com/politics/dr-jill-biden-talks-her-new-campaign-trail-project-and-what-she-learned-about-her-husband/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月，吉尔和丈夫在一段影片中提到[[2019冠状病毒病疫情对教育的影响|2019冠状病毒病疫情对教育的影响]]，表示理解学生、家长和老师对线上教育替代方案感到沮丧的心情，但表示“学校和家长一个明确、有科学依据的策略，而不是混杂的信息和最后通牒”<ref>{{cite news | url=https://news.yahoo.com/biden-outlines-school-reopening-plan-194338722.html | title=Biden outlines school reopening plan amid pandemic | agency=Associated Press | publisher=Yahoo! News | date=2020-07-17 | access-date=2020-07-18 | archive-date=2020-07-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718105836/https://news.yahoo.com/biden-outlines-school-reopening-plan-194338722.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。她批评教育部长[[贝琪·德沃斯|贝琪·德沃斯]]为了政治目的重新开放学校，不考虑后果，表示“（拜登上台）第一件事就是要选一位在公立学校担任教师、课堂经验丰富的人士担任教育部长”，不要出现德沃斯这样的人<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/politics/jill-biden-promises-if-bidens-elected-no-more-betsy-devos/ar-BB16xtQs | title=Jill Biden promises if Biden's elected 'no more Betsy DeVos' | author-first=Tal | author-last=Axelrod | publisher=MSN | date=2020-07-09 | access-date=2020-07-18 | archive-date=2020-07-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718110751/https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/politics/jill-biden-promises-if-bidens-elected-no-more-betsy-devos/ar-BB16xtQs | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

吉尔也热情参与副总统候选人的选拔过程。{{tsl|en|2020 Democratic National Convention|2020年民主党全国大会}}第二个晚上，拜登在布兰迪万高中（{{lang|en|Brandywine High School}}）的教室发表讲话，这是她曾教过英文的学校<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/18/us/elections/jill-biden-returns-to-her-old-classroom-to-deliver-a-convention-speech.html | title=Jill Biden returns to her old classroom to deliver a convention speech | author-first=Katie | author-last=Glueck | newspaper=The New York Times | date=2020-08-18 | access-date=2020-08-21 | archive-date=2020-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820182944/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/18/us/elections/jill-biden-returns-to-her-old-classroom-to-deliver-a-convention-speech.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。讲话中，她将家庭困难与国家困境进行比较，表示让破碎家庭完整如同让国家完整，需要用到关爱、理解，用到小善举、勇气和坚定的信念<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/08/19/jill-biden-dnc-speech-398335 | title=Jill Biden opens up about family in candid DNC appearance | author-first=Matthew | author-last=Choi | work=Politico | date=2020-08-19 | access-date=2020-08-21 | archive-date=2020-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820233042/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/08/19/jill-biden-dnc-speech-398335 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。大选最后阶段，吉尔在家乡附近的宾夕法尼亚州{{tsl|en|Delaware Valley|特拉华谷}}地区造势，在讲话中强调[[摇摆州|摇摆州]]及女性投票的重要性：“你们要做决定，你们女性要决定这个州的未来，这个州会主宰整场选举”<ref>{{Cite news|last=Do|first=Trang|date=2020-10-08|title=Dr. Jill Biden Campaigns In Delaware, Montgomery Counties, Where 'Women Will Decide The Future Of This State'|publisher=KYW-TV|url=https://philadelphia.cbslocal.com/2020/10/08/dr-jill-biden-campaigns-in-delaware-montgomery-counties/|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-10-10|archive-date=2020-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016204822/https://philadelphia.cbslocal.com/2020/10/08/dr-jill-biden-campaigns-in-delaware-montgomery-counties/}}</ref>。

== 第一夫人 ==
[[File:President_Joe_Biden_swearing_in_ceremony_2.jpg|thumb]]上，吉尔陪同拜登宣誓就任美国总统。]]
2021年1月20日，乔·拜登就任美国总统<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Martin|first1=Jonathan|last2=Burns|first2=Alexander|date=2020-11-07|title=Biden Wins Presidency, Ending Four Tumultuous Years Under Trump|newspaper=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/07/us/politics/biden-election.html|access-date=2020-11-07|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107171052/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/07/us/politics/biden-election.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。吉尔成为[[芭芭拉·布什|芭芭拉·布什]]之后，第一位曾担任第二夫人和第一夫人的总统配偶，也是自[[帕特·尼克松|帕特·尼克松]]后首位非连续担任两个职务的总统配偶。她还会是首位[[意大利裔美国人|意大利裔]]美国第一夫人<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.repubblica.it/dossier/esteri/elezioni-usa-2020-presidenziali-biden-trump/2020/11/07/news/jill_biden_presidenziali_stati_uniti-273533926/ | title=Jill Biden, mai una First Lady italoamericana. Conobbe Joe in un appuntamento al buio | author-first=Alberto Flores | author-last=D'Arcais | newspaper=la Repubblica | date=2020-11-07 | language=it | access-date=2020-11-07 | archive-date=2020-11-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107211955/https://www.repubblica.it/dossier/esteri/elezioni-usa-2020-presidenziali-biden-trump/2020/11/07/news/jill_biden_presidenziali_stati_uniti-273533926/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="isda">{{Cite web|date=2020-11-07|title=Jill Biden Set to Become the First Italian American First Lady|url=https://www.orderisda.org/culture/women/jill-biden-set-to-become-the-first-italian-american-first-lady/|access-date=2020-11-09|publisher=Italian Sons and Daughters of America|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113150952/https://orderisda.org/culture/women/jill-biden-set-to-become-the-first-italian-american-first-lady/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于她表示会继续教书，因此她会是首位在白宫外带薪工作的第一夫人<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/11/12/jill-biden-first-lady-professor-436363 | title=First professor: Jill Biden to make history as a first lady with a day job | author-first=Nicole | author-last=Gaudiano | work=Politico | date=2020-11-12 | access-date=2020-11-14 | archive-date=2020-12-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223210419/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/11/12/jill-biden-first-lady-professor-436363 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年11月，吉尔宣布律师兼外交官{{tsl|en|Julissa Reynoso Pantaleon|朱丽莎·雷诺索·潘塔莱顿}}将担任她的第一夫人幕僚长，拜登竞选团队的安东尼·伯纳尔（{{lang|en|Anthony Bernal}}）将出任高级顾问<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/elections/2020/11/17/joe-biden-trump-transition-live-updates/ | title=Biden names senior staff, receives national security briefing from outside experts | author-first=Felicia | author-last=Sonmez | author2-first=Colby | author2-last=Itkowitz | author3-first=John | author3-last=Wagner | newspaper=The Washington Post | date=2020-11-17 | access-date=2020-11-17 | archive-date=2021-01-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107054131/https://www.washingtonpost.com/elections/2020/11/17/joe-biden-trump-transition-live-updates/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年12月，专栏作家{{le|约瑟夫·爱泼斯坦|Joseph Epstein (writer)}}在《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》发表社论，敦促时任候任第一夫人吉尔放弃[[博士|博士]]（Doctor）头衔，因为她不是医生（英文也叫Doctor）<ref>{{cite news |last1=Epstein |first1=Joseph |title=Opinion: Is There a Doctor in the White House? Not if You Need an M.D. |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/is-there-a-doctor-in-the-white-house-not-if-you-need-an-m-d-11607727380 |newspaper=The Wall Street Journal |date=2020-12-11 |accessdate=2021-01-19 |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117195534/https://www.wsj.com/articles/is-there-a-doctor-in-the-white-house-not-if-you-need-an-m-d-11607727380 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，然而这番言论遭到广泛批评，尤其是职业女性<ref>{{cite news | url=https://abcnews.go.com/GMA/News/women-rally-jill-biden-controversial-op-ed-calls/story?id=74713599 | title=Women rally around Jill Biden after controversial op-ed calls for future first lady to drop 'Dr.' | author-first=Katie | author-last=Kindelan | publisher=ABC News | date=2020-12-14 | accessdate=2021-01-19 | archive-date=2021-01-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111041717/https://abcnews.go.com/GMA/News/women-rally-jill-biden-controversial-op-ed-calls/story?id=74713599 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2021年美国总统就职典礼|2021年美国总统就职典礼]]当天，即将卸任的第一夫人[[梅拉尼娅·特朗普|梅拉尼娅·特朗普]]未依照传统邀请吉尔到白宫茶叙<ref>{{cite web |last1=Oliver |first1=O'Connell |title=Ashley Biden confirms Melania snubbed her mother on White House handover |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/ashley-biden-melania-white-house-inauguration-b1789636.html |website=The Independent |accessdate=2021-01-28 |date=2021-01-19 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119192153/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/ashley-biden-melania-white-house-inauguration-b1789636.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[Image:President_Joe_Biden_and_First_Lady_Jill_Biden_serve_an_early_Thanksgiving_meal_to_service_members_and_military_families_at_Fort_Bragg.jpg|thumb]]军事基地，出席军队感恩节聚餐活动]]
吉尔计划在上任后重推与奥巴马时期第一夫人米歇尔·奥巴马共同推出的军属计划“加入部队”（Joining Forces）。该项目被特朗普时期第一夫人梅拉尼娅搁置。此外，拜登循线上途径向军人家属了解情况<ref>{{cite news |last1=Chalfant |first1=Morgan |last2=Manchester |first2=Julia |date=2021-02-20 |title=Jill Biden picks up where she left off |url=https://thehill.com/homenews/administration/539687-jill-biden-picks-up-where-she-left-off |work=The Hill |access-date=2021-02-21 |archive-date=2021-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319160401/https://thehill.com/homenews/administration/539687-jill-biden-picks-up-where-she-left-off |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在华盛顿州[[路易斯–麥克喬德聯合基地|路易斯–麥克喬德聯合基地]]和{{le|惠德比岛海军航空站|Naval Air Station Whidbey Island}}视察时，吉尔强调要照顾好军人家属，表扬联合基地设立开辟专门空间[[自闭症谱系|自闭症患儿]]设立专门的照顾空间<ref>{{cite news|last1=Brunner|first1=Jim|last2=Leshikar|first2=Maya|date=2021-03-09|title=First lady Jill Biden visits Washington military bases in support of families|url=https://www.seattletimes.com/seattle-news/politics/first-lady-jill-biden-visits-washington-military-bases-in-support-of-families/|newspaper=The Seattle Times|accessdate=2022-03-16|archive-date=2021-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211011084616/https://www.seattletimes.com/seattle-news/politics/first-lady-jill-biden-visits-washington-military-bases-in-support-of-families/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

吉尔继续在北弗吉尼亚社区学院教书，利用[[Zoom|Zoom]]向受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影响无法面授的学生授课。考虑到安全原因以及部分学生要求加课的呼声，授课人名字为“职员”（staff），而不是吉尔·拜登<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/education/jill-biden-professor/2021/01/12/c5ec4a74-4ea3-11eb-bda4-615aaefd0555_story.html|title=Most people know her as Jill Biden. But to some she is Dr. B, the compassionate and challenging educator who went the extra mile.|date=2018-06-18|website=Washington Post|language=en|access-date=2021-01-12|archive-date=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319160441/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/education/jill-biden-professor/2021/01/12/c5ec4a74-4ea3-11eb-bda4-615aaefd0555_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine | url=https://people.com/politics/joe-jill-biden-first-white-house-interview/ | title=In First White House Interview, Joe & Jill Biden Talk Marriage, Family, Prayer – and the Challenges Ahead | author-first=Sandra Sobieraj | author-last=Westfall | magazine=People | date=2021-02-03 | access-date=2021-03-08 | archive-date=2021-03-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319160411/https://people.com/politics/joe-jill-biden-first-white-house-interview/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。为了检查学生作业，吉尔经常熬夜<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/02/20/politics/jill-biden-first-lady-agenda/index.html | title=Jill Biden is hitting the ground running – in all directions | author-first=Kate | author-last=Bennett | publisher=CNN | date=2021-02-20 | access-date=2021-03-08 | archive-date=2021-03-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319160435/https://www.cnn.com/2021/02/20/politics/jill-biden-first-lady-agenda/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年9月，吉尔重返北弗吉尼亚社区学院面授课堂<ref name="nyt-in-person">{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/09/07/us/politics/jill-biden-teaching.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210907180122/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/09/07/us/politics/jill-biden-teaching.html |archive-date=2021-09-07 |subscription=yes | title=The First Lady Is Back in the Classroom | author-first=Katie | author-last=Rogers | newspaper=The New York Times | date=September 8, 2021 | page=A11}}</ref>，体现拜登政府期盼学生及老师回归实体教学的愿望<ref name="nyt-in-person"/>。开展教学工作的同时，吉尔还积极游说立法机构通过[[重建美好未来方案|美国家庭计划]]方案，向有需要的学生提供免费就读社区大学的机会<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.politico.com/news/2021/04/28/jill-biden-community-college-tuition-484979 | title=Jill Biden leading the way on community college tuition coverage, Biden says | author-first=Jasmine | author-last=Hilton | work=Politico | date=2021-04-28 | accessdate=2022-03-16 | archive-date=2022-02-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220208121425/https://www.politico.com/news/2021/04/28/jill-biden-community-college-tuition-484979 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。该计划后来纳入社会支出计划《重建美好未来方案》，成本初步预估达1000亿美元<ref name="nbcn-dropped"/>。然而方案谈判过程举步维艰，未能得到参议院民主党人的普遍支持<ref name="nbcn-dropped"/>。尽管如此，吉尔还是继续提倡免费就读社区大学计划，而国会民主党人也计划在《重建方案》被否决后继续推动该倡议<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.usnews.com/news/education-news/articles/2021-10-19/house-democrats-rally-to-preserve-biden-plans-free-community-college-provision | title=House Democrats Rally to Preserve Biden Plan's Free Community College Provision | author-first=Lauren | author-last=Camera | newspaper=U.S. News & World Report | date=2021-10-19 | accessdate=2022-03-16 | archive-date=2022-02-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220208121425/https://www.usnews.com/news/education-news/articles/2021-10-19/house-democrats-rally-to-preserve-biden-plans-free-community-college-provision | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2022年2月，在社区大学全国立法峰会（Community College National Legislative Summit）前的公开活动中，吉尔承认免费就读社区大学可能会从《重建方案》中剔除，表示自己对此“感到失望.......因为这些东西在我看来不是法案和预算”<ref name="nbcn-dropped">{{cite news | url=https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/first-lady-jill-biden-say-free-community-college-wont-included-social-rcna15128 | title=Jill Biden says free community college won't be included in social spending bill | author-first=Rebecca | author-last=Shabad | publisher=NBC News | date=2022-02-07 | accessdate=2022-03-16 | archive-date=2022-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220303140214/https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/first-lady-jill-biden-say-free-community-college-wont-included-social-rcna15128 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2022年5月，吉尔访问临近{{le|斯洛伐克-乌克兰边境|Slovakia–Ukraine border|斯洛伐克边境}}的乌克兰城市[[乌日霍罗德|乌日霍罗德]]，在乌克兰第一夫人[[葉蓮娜·澤連斯卡婭|葉蓮娜·澤連斯卡婭]]的陪同下慰问因[[2022年俄罗斯入侵乌克兰|俄罗斯入侵行动]]流离失所的乌克兰学童。慰问当天适逢[[母亲节|母亲节]]，吉尔表示自己特意在这个日子到访<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/jill-biden-ukraine-surprise-visit-first-lady/ | title=First lady Dr. Jill Biden makes surprise visit to Ukraine | author-first=Melissa | author-last=Quinn | publisher=CBS News | date=2022-05-08}}</ref>。

